<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= siteName %> - Terms and Services</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/authentication/terms.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1><%= siteName %> Terms and Services</h1>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>1. Agreement to Terms</h2>
            <p>By accessing and using <%= siteName %>, you agree to be bound by these Terms and Services. If you disagree with any part of these terms, you may not access our website or use our services.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>2. Products and Services</h2>
            <p>Our website offers clothing and fashion accessories for sale. All products are subject to availability. We reserve the right to discontinue any product at any time.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>All product descriptions are accurate to the best of our knowledge</li>
                <li>Colors may vary slightly from what appears on your screen</li>
                <li>Sizing information is provided in product descriptions</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>3. Pricing and Payment</h2>
            <p>All prices are listed in <%= currency %> and are subject to change without notice. Payment must be made through our approved payment methods. We use secure payment processing systems to protect your information.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>4. Shipping and Delivery</h2>
            <p>We ship to the locations listed in our shipping policy. Delivery times may vary depending on your location. Shipping costs will be calculated at checkout.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>5. Returns and Refunds</h2>
            <p>Our return policy allows returns within <%= returnPeriod %> days of purchase. Items must be unused and in original packaging. Please see our Returns Policy for complete details.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>6. Privacy Policy</h2>
            <p>Your privacy is important to us. Please review our Privacy Policy to understand how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>7. Intellectual Property</h2>
            <p>All content on this website, including images, text, and logos, is the property of <%= siteName %> and is protected by copyright laws.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-info">
            <p>If you have any questions about these Terms and Services, please contact us at:</p>
            <p>Email: <%= contactEmail %></p>
            <p>Phone: <%= contactPhone %></p>
        </div>

        <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: <%= lastUpdated %></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>